'''通济隆集团'''（{{lang-en|Travelex Group}}）是一家总部位于伦敦的外汇交易公司，由{{link-en|Lloyd Dorfman|Lloyd Dorfman}}创立。该公司的主要业务包括国际支付、货币兑换和发行供旅行者使用的预存款卡。<ref name=TravelexOfficial>[http://www.travelex.co.uk/group/default.asp Travelex Group information] {{Wayback|url=http://www.travelex.co.uk/group/default.asp |date=20100819140742 }} on official website, accessed 5 November 2012.</ref> Travelex是世界上最大的{{link-en|外汇经纪商|Foreign exchange companies}}。<ref>Brown, Mark [http://www.guardian.co.uk/stage/2010/oct/28/national-theatre-dorfman-donation "National Theatre's Cottesloe venue to be renamed after £10m donor"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/stage/2010/oct/28/national-theatre-dorfman-donation |date=20120913073201 }} ''[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]'' 28 October 2010.  Retrieved 7 December 2010.</ref>

在2007年的一次[[病毒营销|病毒营销]]中，该公司提出了一种叫做“宇宙银河间准货币单位”的太空货币。<ref name="quidpr">{{Cite web|url=http://www.travelex.co.uk/press/ENG/DOC_QUID_10042007.asp|title=Travelex Press Release|accessdate=October 9, 2007|publisher=Travelex|year=2007|author=Travelex|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804162033/https://www.travelex.co.uk/press/ENG/DOC_QUID_10042007.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="bbc">{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/china/lifeintheuk/story/2007/10/071008_space_currency.shtml|title=科学家设计出太空货币|accessdate=2013-11-18|publisher=BBC China|year=2007|archive-date=2017-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170906012937/http://www.bbc.co.uk/china/lifeintheuk/story/2007/10/071008_space_currency.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
1976年，Dorfman创立了Travelex，第一个分部在伦敦中部开业。<ref name=TravelexOfficial></ref>

2000年11月8日，Travelex以4.4亿英镑的价格收购了{{link-en|Thomas Cook AG|Thomas Cook AG}}的全球外汇兑换业务，显著扩展了其国际运作规模。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Travelex+plc+Acquires+Thomas+Cook+Financial+Services+Division;+$630...-a066704076 |title=Travelex plc Acquires Thomas Cook Financial Services Division |author=London(Business Wire) |date=November 8, 2000 |accessdate=January 8, 2011 |archive-date=2019-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190216212100/https://www.thefreelibrary.com/Travelex+plc+Acquires+Thomas+Cook+Financial+Services+Division%3b+%24630...-a066704076 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2005年2月，控制权收购公司[[安佰深|安佰深]]收购了该公司的的多数股份，然而Dorfman保留了30%股份并继续执掌运作。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=newsarchive&sid=aAFSbygVhFJ8 |title=Apax Partners to Buy Majority of Britain's Travelex |publisher=[[Bloomberg_L.P.|Bloomberg]] |date=February 28, 2005 |accessdate=February 1, 2011 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924142638/http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=newsarchive&sid=aAFSbygVhFJ8 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在出任{{link-en|Wolseley plc|Wolseley plc}}的CEO之前，{{link-en|Ian Meakins|Ian Meakins}}曾于2006年至2009年间任Travelex的CEO。

2010年初Travelex公布了由于支付大额债务利息导致的显著亏损。前一年Travelex已经撤回了一项上市计划并表示现在在考虑一系列可能的财产结构。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.thisismoney.co.uk/markets/article.html?in_article_id=513210&in_page_id=3 |title=Travelex in race to sort out huge debt |publisher=thisismoney.co.uk |date=29 August 2010 |accessdate=4 March 2010 }}</ref>同年Travelex将預付卡管理部門以2.9亿英镑售予[[万事达|万事达]]来减轻债务。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/banksandfinance/8192623/MasterCard-buys-Travelex-division-for-290m.html |title=MasterCard buys Travelex division for £290m |publisher=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Telegraph]] |date=9 December 2010 |location=London |first=Harry |last=Wilson |accessdate=2014-07-14 |archive-date=2018-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181123201021/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/banksandfinance/8192623/MasterCard-buys-Travelex-division-for-290m.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-09/travelex-loans-rise-on-plans-to-cut-senior-debt-after-unit-sale.html?cmpid=msnmoney |title=Travelex Loans Rise on Plans to Cut Senior Debt After Unit Sale |publisher=[[Bloomberg_L.P.|Bloomberg]] |date=December 10, 2010 |author=Patricia Kuo |accessdate=February 1, 2011 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714160825/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-09/travelex-loans-rise-on-plans-to-cut-senior-debt-after-unit-sale.html?cmpid=msnmoney |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=萬事達卡以4.58億美元 收購Travelex預付卡業務|url=http://news.cts.com.tw/cnyes/money/201012/201012100628248.html|accessdate=2014-07-14|newspaper=華視新聞網|date=2010-12-10|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714222841/http://news.cts.com.tw/cnyes/money/201012/201012100628248.html|archivedate=2014-07-14}}</ref>

2011年7月5日，Travelex将其全球支付解决方案部门以6.06亿英镑的价格出售给[[西联汇款|西联汇款]]。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20110705005742/en/Western-Union-Acquire-Travelex-Global-Business-Payments |title=Western Union to Acquire Travelex Global Business Payments |publisher=Businesswire |date=July 5, 2011 |accessdate=2014-07-14 |archive-date=2020-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200128184322/https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20110705005742/en/Western-Union-Acquire-Travelex-Global-Business-Payments |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://tech.ifeng.com/internet/detail_2011_07/06/7458549_0.shtml |title=快讯：西联汇款收购Travelex旗下部门 |publisher=凤凰网 |date=2011-07-06 |accessdate=2014-07-14 |archive-date=2019-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191111171253/http://tech.ifeng.com/internet/detail_2011_07/06/7458549_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

截至2014年3月，Travelex在27个国家运作，拥有超过1500个分支。<ref>{{cite web|author=Travelex|title=Travelex Corporate Presentation|url=http://www.travelex-corporate.com/uploadedFiles/Corporate/Static_Pages/Resources/20141205Corporatepresentationupdated160514.pdf|work=2014-03|accessdate=2014-07-14|archive-date=2019-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190819114028/http://www.travelex-corporate.com/uploadedFiles/Corporate/Static_Pages/Resources/20141205Corporatepresentationupdated160514.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年，安佰深将股份售予位于阿联酋的印度商人{{link-en|Bavaguthu Raghuram Shetty|B. R. Shetty|B. R. Shetty}}。Shetty拥有在32个国家运作的阿联酋汇款公司{{link-en|UAE Exchange|UAE Exchange}}。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.theguardian.com/business/2014/may/23/apax-travelex-bavaguthu-shetty-centurion-investments-foreign-exchange |title=Apax to sell majority stake in Travelex |date=May 23, 2014 |publisher=The Guardian |accessdate=2014-07-14 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305032657/http://www.theguardian.com/business/2014/may/23/apax-travelex-bavaguthu-shetty-centurion-investments-foreign-exchange |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Travelex shelves IPO during sale talks with UAE buyer |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/banksandfinance/10849784/Travelex-shelves-IPO-during-sale-talks-with-UAE-buyer.html |date=May 22, 2014 |publisher=The Telegraph |accessdate=2014-07-14 |archive-date=2020-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200128185218/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/banksandfinance/10849784/Travelex-shelves-IPO-during-sale-talks-with-UAE-buyer.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

